{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of text area","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSTextArea","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"TextAreaComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"text area"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text area"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for text area component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the text area component tokens you want.","","        override var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingBlockXl }","        override var sizeMinHeightInput: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._1000 }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: TextAreaComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own space and size semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider(","                                            sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                            spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.17.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProviderC","roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:spaces:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"